  "A tax benefit for homeowners": "",
  "The interest earned on a savings account": "",
  "An increase in the value of an asset": "",
  "Depreciation is the reduction in value of a tangible asset over its useful life. Cars, equipment, and technology typically lose value over time, modeled as exponential decay.": "",
